title: GET_PLAYER_ROUTING_BUCKET
content:
0x52441C34// GetPlayerRoutingBucket
int GET_PLAYER_ROUTING_BUCKET(char* playerSrc);Parameters:playerSrc: The player to get the routing bucket for.Returns: The routing bucket ID.Gets the routing bucket for the specified player.Routing buckets are also known as 'dimensions' or 'virtual worlds' in past echoes, however they are population-aware.
